OPINIONPLUS — Every voice, a masthead\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"A platform to tell your story, with your name and logo at the top, and the tools to build an audience around your truth.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.opinionplus.online\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"OPINIONPLUS\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.opinionplus.online/og-image.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"OPINIONPLUS — Every voice, a masthead\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"OPINIONPLUS — Every voice, a masthead\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"A platform to tell your story, with your name and logo at the top, and the tools to build an audience around your truth.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.opinionplus.online/og-image.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-body bg-paper text-ink min-h-screen flex flex-col antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"border-b border-wire bg-paper/95 backdrop-blur sticky top-0 z-40\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-baseline gap-2 group\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"editorial-h text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline wire-tag\">every voice, a masthead</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium\"><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Feed</a><a class=\"btn-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-sm\" href=\"/login\">Sign in</a></nav><button class=\"md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16\"><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">About</p><h1 class=\"editorial-h text-4xl font-bold mb-8\">Every voice deserves a masthead.</h1><div class=\"prose-story text-ink-700 text-[1.05rem]\"><p>Most platforms ask you to shrink your story to fit a feed. OpinionPlus starts from the opposite instinct: your name goes at the top, your logo sits beside it, and the page belongs to you before it belongs to an algorithm.</p><p>We built OpinionPlus for the journalist without a masthead, the filmmaker without a distributor, and the person who simply has something true to say and nowhere that feels like theirs to say it. A story here isn&#x27;t a post lost in a scroll — it&#x27;s a publication with your byline, your archive, and readers who chose to follow you specifically.</p><p>That&#x27;s the whole idea, really. Give people the tools a real publisher would have — logo, profile, engagement, an audience — and get out of the way. The stories are yours. We just built the newsroom.</p><p>OpinionPlus is moderated, not policed. Admins exist to handle abuse and false reports, not to referee opinions. If your story is true and it&#x27;s yours, it belongs here.</p></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-wire mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"sm:col-span-2\"><a class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-extrabold hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></a><p class=\"text-sm text-ink-400 mt-2 max-w-xs\">A platform where every person gets a masthead — their name, their logo, their truth, at the top of the page.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-5\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/opinionplus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"X (Twitter)\" class=\"w-9 h-9 grid place-items-center rounded-full border border-wire text-ink-600 hover:text-signal hover:border-signal transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-twitter\"><path d=\"M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://instagram.com/opinionplus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"Instagram\" class=\"w-9 h-9 grid place-items-center rounded-full border border-wire text-ink-600 hover:text-signal hover:border-signal transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-instagram\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"20\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\" rx=\"5\" ry=\"5\"></rect><path d=\"M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z\"></path><line x1=\"17.5\" x2=\"17.51\" y1=\"6.5\" y2=\"6.5\"></line></svg></a><a href=\"https://linkedin.com/company/opinionplus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\" class=\"w-9 h-9 grid place-items-center rounded-full border border-wire text-ink-600 hover:text-signal hover:border-signal transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-linkedin\"><path d=\"M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z\"></path><rect width=\"4\" height=\"12\" x=\"2\" y=\"9\"></rect><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></a><a href=\"/feed.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"RSS feed\" class=\"w-9 h-9 grid place-items-center rounded-full border border-wire text-ink-600 hover:text-signal hover:border-signal transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rss\"><path d=\"M4 11a9 9 0 0 1 9 9\"></path><path d=\"M4 4a16 16 0 0 1 16 16\"></path><circle cx=\"5\" cy=\"19\" r=\"1\"></circle></svg></a></div></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Read</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Feed</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About OpinionPlus</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/publish\">Publish your story</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Legal &amp; support</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"rule\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-5 justify-between\"><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-1\">Stay in the loop</p><p class=\"text-sm text-ink-400 max-w-sm\">The week&#x27;s sharpest bylines, straight to your inbox. No spam, unsubscribe anytime.</p></div><form noValidate=\"\" class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto\"><div class=\"flex-1 sm:w-72\"><input type=\"email\" inputMode=\